Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss, the beginning\Nis red and black passions{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.60,0:00:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometimes, we rely on our contrary hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.77,0:00:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss, the last resort is a\Nmission which changes the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.10,0:00:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is no place for\Nambiguous answers in love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even while pretending not to\Nsee the impossible reality, we bet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.48,0:00:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hard-to-obtain-truth\NCan you feel me now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.44,0:01:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I say to myself,\Nwho gets excited easily?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.48,0:01:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm confused about what to say {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dreamin' the never-waking\Ndream, the falling fate{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't stop lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NYa ya ya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.64,0:01:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I believe in you, even\Nif I lose everything for it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.52,0:01:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NNo no no{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens, what you have\Nto do is take your challengers head-on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.30,0:01:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and become a wall for them to overcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when the time comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you must fight with all\Nyour strength and be defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving your challengers a battle will be\Nanother important duty of yours from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.18,0:02:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla is right. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.43,0:02:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Really even I think that there's no\Nsuch thing as a world without battles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But even now I still sort\Nof think it would be nice{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.55,0:02:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}if there weren't any\Nbattles on the stage at least.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.89,0:02:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Challengers, adventurers, pioneers...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.76,0:02:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All who are called by such names are fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits the fools who\Npursue the dreams no one else dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is either scorn... or applause.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be my dream, Sora. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.51,0:02:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"To the Amazing Promised Place."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay Mom, Dad, I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:02:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken, are you sure it wasn't a burden on\Nyour parents to take in my whole family?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my mom's the one that\Noffered, so it's probably okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess it's all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So tomorrow's the opening day at last, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it looks like they still\Nhaven't finished construction...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It is a pretty big\Nconstruction project, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No big deal, we're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't apologize too lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gave us a job really\Nworth doing. I'm actually grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make this brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did May and Rosetta's\Nmaneuver end up getting okayed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.76,0:03:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The directorial team was supposed\Nto decide at yesterday's rehearsal,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Miss Cathy tested them again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll okay it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.93,0:03:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Rosetta, I'd like a more\Ncommanding presence from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Anna's clown team too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We get to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... I can't breathe... seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That special training was really worth it, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody got their dreams, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't you going to perform anymore, Ken?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I mean, really you\Nwanted to be a performer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So when you found a path\Nas a clown in Anna's team,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought "Hooray! Congratulations!" but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.18,0:04:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not my dream now.\NThat's a dream from a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.10,0:04:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right! I hear\Nour opening show is sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was concerned since\Ncurtain is at an unusual time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now we have one less thing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri was the one who planned\Nthe tie-in with the tour company.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.89,0:05:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well. So he has his\Nfather's sound business sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like he'll make a good partner for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll make my confession...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Confession?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm full of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What? What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were helping me out so much
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because you were entrusting\Nyour own dream to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't get me wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do understand it's really because I'm\Nthe one most hopelessly in need of help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do get it, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But every time I look at it that way, it makes\Nme feel like "Okay, I'll give this my best!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it gives me strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.85,0:05:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I've been letting myself think that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken, it's thanks to you that\NI've been able to come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.22,0:05:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not full of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll become someone who shoulders\Nlots of people's dreams, not just mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:05:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:06:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, shall we go? After all, we\Nhave to get to bed early tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A stage with no battles, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's definitely a ridiculous dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm at the age where I want to\Ntry believing in those foolish dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.53,0:06:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only people who can become true stars
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are the ones who, as they come\Nto realize their dream is foolish,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,believe in it even more and keep pursuing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a very difficult thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everybody called up their own memories
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as if they were being\Nled by Sora's performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The memories of when they wanted\Neverybody to smile, both themselves and others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a true Kaleido Star's maneuver,\None Sora arrived at on her own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure all the audience's\Nhearts will become one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that's right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I don't think is right
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is that you were practicing the\NAngel's Maneuver without even telling {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the apology comes so\Nmeekly it sort of throws me off...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to take my car tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.47,0:07:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already know Sora's going\Nto become a true Kaleido Star,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm not sure it's good for me, who\Nlost, to go looking like I'm her guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you did lose the competition,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.97,0:07:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think to Sora you'll always be\Nthe Layla Hamilton she admires.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.47,0:07:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not go watch her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, why are you so meek today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because your advice is sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I didn't know you thought\Nof me that way. I'm flattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, be that meek\Nafter we get back to Broadway too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I can't promise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought not...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I think you should\Nwatch the show tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling something\Nelse is going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. Something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel's Maneuver jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back Marion, Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's still doing their individual\Npractice, so there's nobody in the dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Then I'll go at it too and--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's seen you trying your best,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they're doing their best to catch up to\Nyou as much as they can, even if it's just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you can take a rest, and believe in everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take a real audition\Nand join the Kaleido Stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.55,0:08:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan says he'll try too,\Nsince he's got nothing to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.72,0:08:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why do you understand him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, do your best tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bye-bye! Take care...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be going now too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A stage without battles, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you always personally\Ninspect the trapezes you'll use.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe we could talk, as two people\Nwho couldn't completely become demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,perhaps I just couldn't leave Sora alone
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.74,0:09:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I saw she couldn't completely\Nbreak herself apart on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On a basic level, the Angel's Maneuver\Nis something that can be performed alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just extra, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those women are strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can run anywhere, all by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But sometimes they want to\Nlean on somebody, just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.76,0:09:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just need to support\Nthem during those times, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our role.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like angels, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess it would make sense\Nthat we couldn't make it as demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manami, Sayaka, and Miki say they'll come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Yume will really watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you can't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.14,0:10:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, tomorrow I'll just believe\Nin myself and give it all I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight, Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Angel's Maneuver, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear it's also called "The Fool's Maneuver."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It says Odette fights with the part of her\Nown heart that starts to doubt the prince's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So basically it's about how you have a\Ntough time when you date a popular guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:11:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Odette keeps on believing that\Nthere's an angel heart inside Odile too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty nice, isn't it Yume?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could've done the afternoon showing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack, I can't read this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it going to start soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like, a full house, even\Nthough it's so early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say there's supposed to be a stage event\Ncool enough to warrant an early-morning show.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see your Odette as well, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never stand on this stage again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you invite anyone, Mr. Leon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent Alain passes to\Nthe show and plane tickets,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he might have sold them to buy alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he wouldn't do that... I don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know your old partners will\Ncome too, and get their smiles back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still believe in a stage without battles?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.26,0:11:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to believe in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary great maneuver is something\Nyou can't do unless you believe in it absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm sure the Angel's\NManeuver is the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I'm sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I said Layla was a lukewarm performer,\Nyou told me to apologize, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she'd retired after pulling off\Nthe legendary great maneuver with you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.64,0:12:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so she could keep that glory forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Layla mastered the Angel's Maneuver\Nand came back, fully prepared to lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For my sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't fought Layla that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your confidence most likely\Nwouldn't be as firm as it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:13:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please raise the curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all get the very best applause together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is Scene 5. Odette\Nis going to meet the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The prince falls in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a nice expression on his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The material is good, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scene 11: The ball. Anna's clown team is on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. Anna's looking good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time at last for her special\Ntraining to be put to the test!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.47,0:14:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They like it... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing there, but it looks\Nlike she's being pulled by a string!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This laughter is for me! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:15:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I finally got it, Papa, Mama... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next it's Demon Lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The prince has his heart stolen by Odile!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Odile is the demon heart. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mysterious and bold, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}more lively than Odette! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.14,0:15:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big sister, you look so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Change the backdrop to the deep forest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Odile leads the prince into the\Ndeep forest and is trapped there as well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Odette discovers\Nthe conflict in Odile's heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The fairy that leads Odile\Nback from her mistaken path...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm counting on you, Rosetta. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The very best applause,\Ntogether with everyone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here we go. Eternal Illusion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal Illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Thanks, May.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.51,0:16:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's finally time. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scene 32. The angel's flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's believe in Sora's angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three minutes to go. Please open the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora's going to become an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O Fool,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,go forth believing that what\Nawaits you in the end is applause!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:17:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:18:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a success. Please lower the Angel Trapezes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.39,0:18:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll show my angel heart to everyone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I pray that everyone\Nwho came to see this show...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That everyone's angel hearts become one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's mysterious... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I always thought of a show as an ordeal\Nto be gotten through as quickly as possible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But when I'm flying through the\Nair matching Sora's movements,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}each moment starts to seem precious.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every moment seems irreplaceably precious...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to like the\Nstage a lot more too, Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:19:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I become a true star,\NI'm sure you'll change too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Leon, on the stage no\Nmoment is ever the same twice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's never anything but the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll live in the\Npresent with all my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that no matter what\Nhappens, I'll have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophie, I finally understand your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be on this stage.\NI want to perform with Sora, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow I just can't stand still.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May! Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what a true star is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.43,0:20:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can such a thing be real?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the performers\Nwho have stormed the stage
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are acting in harmony,\Nwithout instructions from anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the stage Sora dreamed of.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.64,0:21:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here, in this moment, a stage\Nwith no battles definitely exists.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've seen your miracle, Sora. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My role is over, then. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:23.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The dream everyone is\Nlooking for must be someplace{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.93,0:21:26.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It has to be somewhere {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:34.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until your wish comes true\Nsomeday, you're not alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.22,0:21:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've seen it through, Sora... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.85,0:21:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What you were aiming for,\Nthe show of a true Kaleido Star.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.64,0:21:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora! You're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.18,0:22:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the dream's crossed the finish line...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.35,0:22:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little sad that it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.05,0:22:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is the starting line of a new dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.89,0:22:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.68,0:22:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.72,0:22:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is it all right if I keep on\Nthinking of myself as your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.05,0:22:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. You're not my dream anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.76,0:22:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.18,0:22:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.35,0:22:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.76,0:22:46.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The colors of the evening sun and{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:48.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The wind that I saw that day {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:55.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are still stored away in my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.35,0:23:04.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The truth is I knew all\Nalong, but I couldn't say it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.18,0:23:11.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You alone were beside me the whole time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.51,0:23:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, yesterday I tendered my\Nresignation as Hamilton family maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.60,0:23:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I'll be working to\Nmake a stage debut on Broadway.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.87,0:23:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow me to accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.51,0:23:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.64,0:23:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:32.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The light I haven't seen yet {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:35.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is beaming toward the promised place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.14,0:23:43.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until your wish comes true\Nsomeday, you're not alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.30,0:23:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's just my imagination, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.80,0:23:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so the dream is passed on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.97,0:23:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the next fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.26,0:23:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that all the tickets for the\Nnext two months are already sold!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.55,0:23:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.64,0:23:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.97,0:24:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can be in the show too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.97,0:24:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.51,0:24:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.84,0:24:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like shouting out the\Nname of the maneuver, just tell her so.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.22,0:24:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.30,0:24:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.85,0:24:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My wings are my dream\Nand on towards the sky...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.72,0:24:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
